					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[If alternative extraction procedures were followed, dedicated measures and technologies were used in order to avoid carrying over cellular RNA stabilisation molecules to the final RNA eluate. If stabiliser molecules are carried over, the analytical test reaction may be inhibited.]]></text>
			</staticText>
